        <num>41-3-6</num>
        <content>
          <p>If the action shall be brought by a private citizen and the court shall find that there was no reasonable ground or cause for the action, the cost may be taxed to such citizen.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1917, p. 177, ยง 3; Code 1933, ยง 72-307.)</p>
